    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I bought Delancy  from you at Real Good Food at 3:30 and finished it by 9 pm! I kept exclaiming to my husband &#8220;We have to go to Apizza Scholls! We have to go to Ken&#39;s Artisan Pizza!&#8221; And of course, &#8220;We have to go to Delancy!&#8221;  I so enjoy your transparency as you share Brandon and your story.  It was a pleasure to meet you (and June as the wind blew through her hair and she tried to nibble on your leg!) and see that you are just as real and lovely in person as I thought you would be.  May God continue to bless you and your family on this journey of life together!</p>
