      <p>I just &#8220;devoured&#8221; your book. I read it in a matter of hours. I have followed your blog, read your first book and anxiously awaited Delancey. I was not disappointed!  I am an avid home cook &#038; found myself thrust in the restaurant world &#038; assumed since I was loved to cook, I would love being the GM of a restaurant with very similar sensibilities to that of Delancey. I couldn&#39;t have been more wrong. I can&#39;t tell you how many tears I shed for the year I plodded along in such a foreign land. Thanks for sharing your story. It was a wonderful book and I will be sharing it with many of my friends. </p>
